Creating the request and response classes for the API:-

1. CategoryRequest (Request class for the FetchNextNumber API)

public class CategoryRequest {
    private String categoryCode;
    
    public String getCategoryCode() {
        return categoryCode;
    }

    public void setCategoryCode(String categoryCode) {
        this.categoryCode = categoryCode;
    }
}

2. NumberResponse (Response class for the FetchNextNumber API)

public class NumberResponse {
    private int oldValue;
    private int newValue;

    public NumberResponse(int oldValue, int newValue) {
        this.oldValue = oldValue;
        this.newValue = newValue;
    }
    
    public int getOldValue() {
        return oldValue;
    }

    public void setOldValue(int oldValue) {
        this.oldValue = oldValue;
    }

    public int getNewValue() {
        return newValue;
    }

    public void setNewValue(int newValue) {
        this.newValue = newValue;
    }
}
